CHAIRMAN:<i> Where was he born?</i>

1348
02:20:35.294 --> 02:20:37.261
MICHAEL:<i> Corleone.</i>
<i>Sicily.</i>

1349
02:20:37.296 --> 02:20:39.571
<i>Did he at times use an alias</i>

1350
02:20:39.606 --> 02:20:44.070
<i>that was known in certain</i>
<i>circles as Godfather?</i>

1351
02:20:44.105 --> 02:20:47.238
<i>Godfather is a term that was</i>
<i>used by his friends...</i>

1352
02:20:47.273 --> 02:20:50.780
<i>One of affection.</i>
<i>one of respect.</i>

1353
02:20:50.815 --> 02:20:55.752
<i>Uh. Mr. Chairman.</i>
<i>I would like to verify</i>
<i>the witness' statement.</i>

1354
02:20:55.787 --> 02:21:00.955
<i>For years now. a growing</i>
<i>number of my constituents</i>
<i>have been of Italian descent.</i>

1355
02:21:00.990 --> 02:21:03.760
<i>And I've come to</i>
<i>know them well.</i>

1356
02:21:03.795 --> 02:21:07.962
<i>They have honored me</i>
<i>with their support</i>
<i>and their friendship.</i>

1357
02:21:07.997 --> 02:21:09.832
<i>Indeed. I can proudly say</i>

1358
02:21:09.867 --> 02:21:12.802
<i>that some</i>
<i>of my very best friends</i>
<i>are Italian-Americans.</i>

1359
02:21:14.608 --> 02:21:16.938
<i>However. Mr. Chairman.</i>
<i>at this time unfortunately</i>

1360
02:21:16.973 --> 02:21:19.644
<i>I have to leave</i>
<i>these proceedings</i>

1361
02:21:19.679 --> 02:21:24.682
<i>in order to preside</i>
<i>over a very important</i>
<i>meeting of my own committee.</i>

1362
02:21:24.717 --> 02:21:28.048
<i>But before I leave.</i>
<i>I do want to say this.</i>

1363
02:21:28.083 --> 02:21:29.918
<i>that these</i>
<i>hearings on the Mafia</i>

1364
02:21:29.953 --> 02:21:32.316
<i>are in no way whatsoever</i>

1365
02:21:32.351 --> 02:21:35.055
<i>a slur upon</i>
<i>the great Italian people.</i>

1366
02:21:35.090 --> 02:21:38.223
<i>Because I can state</i>
<i>from my own knowledge</i>
<i>and experience</i>

1367
02:21:38.258 --> 02:21:43.635
<i>that Italian-Americans</i>
<i>are among the most loyal.</i>
<i>most law-abiding.</i>

1368
02:21:43.670 --> 02:21:48.068
<i>patriotic. hard-working</i>
<i>American citizens</i>
<i>in this land.</i>

1369
02:21:48.103 --> 02:21:50.840
<i>It would be a shame.</i>
<i>Mr. Chairman.</i>

1370
02:21:50.875 --> 02:21:53.205
<i>if we allowed</i>
<i>a few rotten apples</i>

1371
02:21:53.240 --> 02:21:55.746
<i>to give a bad name</i>
<i>to the whole barrel.</i>

1372
02:21:55.781 --> 02:21:58.309
<i>Because from the time</i>
<i>of Christopher Columbus</i>

1373
02:21:58.344 --> 02:22:01.213
<i>to the time of Enrico Fermi.</i>

1374
02:22:01.248 --> 02:22:03.688
<i>right up to the present day.</i>

1375
02:22:03.723 --> 02:22:05.690
<i>Italian-Americans</i>
<i>have been pioneers</i>

1376
02:22:05.725 --> 02:22:08.220
<i>in building and defending</i>
<i>our great nation.</i>

1377
02:22:08.255 --> 02:22:10.090
<i>They are the salt</i>
<i>of the earth.</i>

1378
02:22:10.125 --> 02:22:12.763
<i>and one of the backbones</i>
<i>of this country.</i>

1379
02:22:12.798 --> 02:22:15.667
(PEOPLE APPLAUDING)

1380
02:22:19.706 --> 02:22:23.708
CHAIRMAN:
<i>I'm sure we all agree</i>
<i>with our esteemed colleague.</i>

1381
02:22:23.743 --> 02:22:27.877
<i>Now Mr. Corleone.</i>
<i>you have been advised</i>
<i>as to your legal rights.</i>

1382
02:22:27.912 --> 02:22:34.378
<i>We have testimony</i>
<i>from a previous witness.</i>
<i>one Willi Cicci.</i>

1383
02:22:34.413 --> 02:22:38.855
<i>He stated that you are</i>
<i>head of the most powerful</i>
<i>Mafia family in the country.</i>

1384
02:22:38.890 --> 02:22:40.120
<i>Are you?</i>

1385
02:22:40.155 --> 02:22:42.628
MICHAEL:<i> No. I'm not.</i>

1386
02:22:42.663 --> 02:22:44.927
