<i>has testified that you are</i>
<i>personally responsible</i>

1387
02:22:44.962 --> 02:22:48.733
<i>for the murder</i>
<i>of a New York</i>
<i>police captain in 1947</i>

1388
02:22:48.768 --> 02:22:52.297
<i>and with him a man</i>
<i>named Virgil Sollozzo.</i>

1389
02:22:52.332 --> 02:22:53.672
<i>Do you deny this?</i>

1390
02:22:53.707 --> 02:22:55.102
<i>Yes. I do.</i>

1391
02:22:55.137 --> 02:22:58.204
<i>Is it true</i>
<i>that in the year 1950</i>

1392
02:22:58.239 --> 02:23:00.008
<i>you devised the murder</i>

1393
02:23:00.043 --> 02:23:03.781
<i>of the heads of the so-called</i>
<i>"Five Families" in New York</i>

1394
02:23:03.816 --> 02:23:07.378
<i>to assume and consolidate</i>
<i>your nefarious power?</i>

1395
02:23:07.413 --> 02:23:09.182
<i>It's a complete</i>
<i>falsehood.</i>

1396
