<i>hotels in Las Vegas?</i>

1399
02:23:16.796 --> 02:23:20.226
<i>No. it's not true.</i>
<i>I own some stock in</i>
<i>some of the hotels there.</i>

1400
02:23:20.261 --> 02:23:21.865
<i>but very little.</i>

1401
02:23:24.738 --> 02:23:28.872
<i>I also have stock</i>
<i>in IBM and IT&T.</i>

1402
