<i>any interests or control</i>
<i>over gambling and narcotics</i>

1403
02:23:34.440 --> 02:23:36.341
<i>in the state of New York?</i>

1404
02:23:36.376 --> 02:23:38.684
<i>No. I do not.</i>

1405
02:23:38.719 --> 02:23:41.082
<i>Senator. my client would like</i>
<i>to read a statement</i>
<i>before this committee.</i>

1406
